Source: The ink on this page is too faded to make out the words.
Target: 이 페이지의 잉크는 너무 번져서 알아볼 수 없습니다.

Source: These linens are soiled with sweat and blood.
This shovel is broken off at the haft.
This iron wedding band has virtually no value. Its crudely wrought surfaces have been worn smooth by the press of fingers.
Target: 이 철 결혼 반지는 사실상 값어치가 없습니다. 반지의 거친 표면은 손때가 타서 마모되었습니다.

Source: This bound notebook is filled with scrawls in an undecipherable hand.
Target: 이 연습장은 해독할 수 없는 낙서들로 채워져있습니다.

Source: This bound collection of famous Breton sonnets has a partial copy of "The Lusty Argonian Maid" folded between two pages.
Target: 유명한 브레튼 시집 페이지 사이로 \\"음란한 아르고니안 메이드\"\" 복사본이 끼워져있습니다."

Source: The writing on this note is obscured with blood.
There is no longer enough of this soggy bait to use for fishing.
